ion:'bottom-center'})\">â†“ Bottom Center</button><button class='btn btn-secondary btn-sm' onclick=\"ogToast.show('Bottom Right', {position:'bottom-right'})\">â†˜ Bottom Right</button></div><h4 style='margin:2rem 0 1rem;'>Duraciones</h4><div style='display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;'><button class='btn btn-secondary' onclick=\"ogToast.info('Toast rÃ¡pido (1s)', {duration:1000})\">1 segundo</button><button class='btn btn-secondary' onclick=\"ogToast.info('Toast normal (3s)', {duration:3000})\">3 segundos</button><button class='btn btn-secondary' onclick=\"ogToast.info('Toast largo (5s)', {duration:5000})\">5 segundos</button></div></div>"
